\pard\sb300\sa200\keep\keepn\b\f1\fs32\cf2 1. \tab ABSTRACT\par
\pard\sb150\sa200\b0\f0\fs22\cf1 The Teacher Job Portal is a \b centralized, domain-specific recruitment and talent management platform\b0\ designed for schools, colleges, training institutes, and freelance educators. It enables institutions to publish structured vacancies and manage candidate lifecycles while empowering teachers to showcase comprehensive professional profiles and apply efficiently.\par
\pard\sa200\fs22 Core capabilities include \i job posting and moderation, advanced filtering, multilingual interface\i0\ (11 Indian languages), secure document handling, application status tracking, real-time notifications, analytics dashboards, and a \b scalable architecture\b0\ prepared for AI-driven matching. Emphasis is placed on \b usability, transparency, performance, security,\b0\ and future extensibility.\par
\pard\sa400\par

